headline: JPMorgan Keeps Neutral on EMR but Raises Target Ahead of Q4 Earnings
summary: Emerson Electric Co. (NYSE:EMR) is included among the 13 Best Dividend Kings to Buy in 2026. On January 16, JPMorgan analyst Stephen Tusa raised JPMorgan’s price target on Emerson Electric Co. (NYSE:EMR) to $157 from $150, while keeping a Neutral rating on the stock. The change was part of the bank’s broader Q4 earnings preview […]
